      "span_text": "F-actin accumulates in clusters and, although we do not know their nature (the phospho-myosin signal was too weak at this stage to confirm with confidence its presence at these sites), it is tempting to speculate by analogy with other systems  ) that they represent structures under tension involved in restricting cell rearrangements."
